2009;;Leslie, My Name Is Evil;;Canadian;;Reginald Harkema;;Kristen Hager, Gregory Smith, Ryan Robbins, Tracy Wright, Don McKellar;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leslie,_My_Name_Is_Evil;;Leslie is a troubled 1960s teenager who eventually becomes a follower of Charles Manson and is charged, convicted, and sentenced to death in August 1969 for the murders of Leno and Rosemary LaBianca. The story revolves around how a young juror, Perry, becomes infatuated with Leslie during her trial.